  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "chapterTitle": "第一讲 史学精神和史学方法",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "23523078_7_9457-9516",
          "range": "9457-9516",
          "rangeStart": 9457,
          "rangeEnd": 9516,
          "markText": "我认为今天的我们，批评中国，指斥中国，都是在讲历史，而实际则都不是历史。只把眼前的病态来当整部历史看，这是最大一错误。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1741822118,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-03-13 07:28:38",
          "chapterUid": 7,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23523078&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=9457&rangeEnd=9516",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/da7327b07166ef06da7f196?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=9457&rangeEnd=9516"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "23523078_7_2666-2696",
          "range": "2666-2696",
          "rangeStart": 2666,
          "rangeEnd": 2696,
          "markText": "历史时间过去的未过去，依然存在着；未来的早来到，也早存在着。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1741822058,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-03-13 07:27:38",
          "chapterUid": 7,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23523078&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2666&rangeEnd=2696",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/da7327b07166ef06da7f196?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2666&rangeEnd=2696"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "chapterTitle": "第三讲 中国历史上的经济",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "23523078_9_12756-12847",
          "range": "12756-12847",
          "rangeStart": 12756,
          "rangeEnd": 12847,
          "markText": "今天中国人的大缺点，就在把自己本身的社会实相撇过不谈，而专门滥用西洋几个空名词套上，硬拼硬凑，硬要叫中国来做別人家文化的殖民地。我们希望中国文化还要自觉的站起来，那么中国才有新希望。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1741822083,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-03-13 07:28:03",
          "chapterUid": 9,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23523078&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=12756&rangeEnd=12847",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/da7327b07166ef06da7f196?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=12756&rangeEnd=12847"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "23523078_9_822-877",
          "range": "822-877",
          "rangeStart": 822,
          "rangeEnd": 877,
          "markText": "倘若个人或社会，把经济当作唯一最重要的事件与问题，那么这个人的人生决非最理想的人生，这社会也决非最理想的社会。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1741822069,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-03-13 07:27:49",
          "chapterUid": 9,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23523078&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=822&rangeEnd=877",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/da7327b07166ef06da7f196?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=822&rangeEnd=877"
